org.paces.Stata.Google

Class GoogleStataVars

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.paces.Stata.Google.GoogleStataVars

  • public class GoogleStataVars
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to construct variables, variable labels, and retrieve variable indices used by the different return types from the Google geocode API.
    Version:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    Billy Buchanan
